{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-01-binary-count","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"1","topic":"Системы счисления","prototype_id":"ege_number_systems_binary_count","skill_atoms":["number_systems","binary_representation","count_digits"],"difficulty_level":"basic","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-01-binary-count","statement_md":"Значение выражения 64 + 32 + 8 + 1 записали в двоичной системе счисления. Сколько единиц содержится в этой записи?","answer":["4"],"solution_md":"64 + 32 + 8 + 1 = 105 = 1101001_2. В записи четыре единицы.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-02-logic-truth","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"2","topic":"Логика","prototype_id":"ege_logic_truth_table","skill_atoms":["logic","truth_tables","implication"],"difficulty_level":"basic","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-02-logic-truth","statement_md":"Для скольких наборов значений переменных x и y истинно выражение (x -> y) AND x? В ответе запишите только число наборов.","answer":["1"],"solution_md":"Если выражение истинно и содержит AND x, то x = 1. При x = 1 импликация x -> y истинна только при y = 1. Подходит один набор.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-05-executor","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"5","topic":"Исполнитель","prototype_id":"ege_executor_linear","skill_atoms":["executor","algorithm_trace"],"difficulty_level":"basic","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-05-executor","statement_md":"Исполнитель Калькулятор имеет две команды: 1) прибавь 2; 2) умножь на 3. Начальное число равно 4. Программа 121 преобразует число. Какое число получится?","answer":["20"],"solution_md":"Старт 4. Команда 1: 6. Команда 2: 18. Команда 1: 20.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-07-file-size","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"7","topic":"Кодирование информации","prototype_id":"ege_file_size_audio","skill_atoms":["information_units","file_size"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-07-file-size","statement_md":"Аудиофайл длится 20 секунд, записан в моно режиме с частотой дискретизации 8000 Гц и глубиной кодирования 8 бит. Определите размер файла в байтах без учёта заголовка.","answer":["160000"],"solution_md":"20 * 8000 * 8 = 1 280 000 бит. Делим на 8 и получаем 160 000 байт.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-08-combinatorics","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"8","topic":"Комбинаторика","prototype_id":"ege_words_no_repeat","skill_atoms":["combinatorics","counting"],"difficulty_level":"basic","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-08-combinatorics","statement_md":"Сколько различных трёхбуквенных слов можно составить из букв A, B, C, D, если буквы в слове не повторяются?","answer":["24"],"solution_md":"На первую позицию 4 варианта, на вторую 3, на третью 2. Всего 4 * 3 * 2 = 24.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-11-password","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"11","topic":"Количество информации","prototype_id":"ege_password_storage","skill_atoms":["information_units","alphabet_power","ceil_bits"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-11-password","statement_md":"Пароль состоит из 12 символов. Каждый символ выбирают из алфавита мощностью 20. Для хранения каждого символа используют минимальное одинаковое целое число бит. Сколько байт нужно для хранения 10 таких паролей?","answer":["75"],"solution_md":"Для 20 символов нужно 5 бит на символ, так как 2^4 < 20 <= 2^5. Один пароль: 12 * 5 = 60 бит. Десять паролей: 600 бит = 75 байт.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-12-string-editor","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"12","topic":"Редактор строк","prototype_id":"ege_string_editor_trace","skill_atoms":["string_editor","algorithm_trace"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-12-string-editor","statement_md":"Редактор получает строку 111222. Пока в строке есть подстрока 12, редактор заменяет первое слева вхождение 12 на 21. Какая строка получится после завершения работы?","answer":["222111"],"solution_md":"Каждая замена передвигает одну двойку левее одной единицы. Процесс сортирует все 2 влево, все 1 вправо. Итог: 222111.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-14-base-equation","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"14","topic":"Системы счисления","prototype_id":"ege_base_equation","skill_atoms":["number_systems","base_conversion"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-14-base-equation","statement_md":"Чему равно десятичное значение числа 231_4? В ответе запишите только число.","answer":["45"],"solution_md":"231_4 = 2 * 4^2 + 3 * 4 + 1 = 32 + 12 + 1 = 45.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-15-interval","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"15","topic":"Логические условия","prototype_id":"ege_logic_interval","skill_atoms":["logic","intervals","predicate"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-15-interval","statement_md":"Найдите наибольшее целое A, при котором выражение (x < 5) OR (x >= A) истинно для любого целого x.","answer":["5"],"solution_md":"Чтобы не было разрыва между условиями x < 5 и x >= A, нужно A <= 5. Наибольшее такое целое A равно 5.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-16-recursion","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"16","topic":"Рекурсия","prototype_id":"ege_recursion_trace","skill_atoms":["recursion","trace"],"difficulty_level":"basic","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-16-recursion","statement_md":"Функция F(n) задана так: F(1)=1; при n > 1 F(n)=F(n-1)+2. Найдите F(6).","answer":["11"],"solution_md":"Последовательность: 1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 11. F(6)=11.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-23-programs","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"23","topic":"Количество программ","prototype_id":"ege_program_count_dp","skill_atoms":["dynamic_programming","program_count"],"difficulty_level":"medium","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-23-programs","statement_md":"Исполнитель преобразует число на экране. Команды: прибавь 1, прибавь 2. Сколько программ переводят число 3 в число 8?","answer":["8"],"solution_md":"Нужно набрать сумму 5 шагами 1 и 2. Количество способов: f(0)=1, f(1)=1, f(n)=f(n-1)+f(n-2). f(5)=8.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
{"task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-25-divisors","schema_version":"2","learning_track":"ege_informatics","exam":"EGE","task_number":"25","topic":"Поиск делителей","prototype_id":"ege_divisor_search","skill_atoms":["programming","divisors","number_theory"],"difficulty_level":"advanced","source_id":"eduferma_curated_original","source_name":"EduFerma original","source_task_id":"eduferma-original-ege-25-divisors","statement_md":"Сколько натуральных делителей имеет число 84? В ответе запишите только количество делителей.","answer":["12"],"solution_md":"84 = 2^2 * 3^1 * 7^1. Количество делителей: (2+1)(1+1)(1+1)=12.","solution_language":"ru","attachments":[],"verification_status":"verified","license_status":"original","status":"active","created_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T00:00:00Z","subject":"informatics","tags":["curated_seed","original","ege"]}
